@page
@model AboutModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About";
}
<h1 class="display-4">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<div class="text-left border-space">The aim of this web application is sending notifications to targeted users.</div>

<div class="text-left border-space">
    Which are the information you can insert on the home page?
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Text</strong>: <span class="required">required</span>, represents the message body who the user receives into the notification.</li>
        <li><strong>Tag</strong>: <span class="optional">optional</span>, is fundamental to send targeted notifications, represents one or more specific information to identify particular users' categories.</li>
        <ul>
            <li><em>Please note</em>: it's possible to send no one or maximum 10 tags. In this specific use case, send a notification to a specific user inserting only one user id tag (GUID), otherwise send a notification to everyone inserting no tags.</li>
        </ul>
    </ul>
</div>

